{"tid":403217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"chenglap: 華人習慣看到一個「法」字就當成法律, 哪怕是魔法.","createTime":"2017-09-17T04:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T03:55:52.000Z","uid":47714,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"141daf6b348bb678eed30a1fe009a35f6f77c45b","tid":403217,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152059009987357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10152059009987357&d=uGz%2BZe8KJa%2FUzvndc0x6sxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=9aefac02\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152059009987357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者: chenglap<br />\n<br />\n更別說, 中國大陸的憲法經常修改, 香港的反而變成了聖經. 還要是舊約.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152059033767357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10152059033767357&d=uGz%2BZe8KJa%2FUzvndc0x6sxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=a64ef1d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152059033767357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者: chenglap<br />\n<br />\n當然, 我相信大部份人會走向修改基本法, 我不屬於大部份人, 我主張廢除.<br />\n<br />\n憲法是用來約束政府的, 基本上他不是法律. 不過華人習慣看到一個「法」字就當成法律, 哪怕是魔法. 當憲法也約束不了政府時, 他只是一個笑話. 就像國際聯盟成立的用意就是防止世界大戰, 在二次世界大戰發生後, 國際聯盟就是一個浪費錢的笑話."},{"pid":"a4d2493af9202705ec2ae575a8424bd17ddc35e7","tid":403217,"uid":130394,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"佢哋根本唔會諗嘢. 只要有一個人同佢講係唔啱. 佢哋全部都會當曬唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac56e099c2ed7bca8cfa7bef98e53c818e5a51c","tid":403217,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e48bd48e86fa9eede67362e8b6fa142a15a405c5","tid":403217,"uid":130394,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b