http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155605032457357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155605032457357&d=uGz%2BZe8KJa%2FUzvndc0x6sxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=a068fae5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155605032457357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n言論自由不僅容許大學討論香港獨立及臺灣獨立, 亦包括香港任何地方, 任何人討論香港獨立. 而不論你是支持, 反對, 或者純粹討論其可行性, 也是在討論香港獨立. 你主張否定或反對香港獨立, 你也是使用言論自由在討論香港獨立, 都是完全合法的. 基本法是憲制文件, 憲制文件限制公權力. 他基本法亦只限制了政府的公權力實施, 故此基本法只能限制香港政府不能合法地宣佈香港獨立, 以及不能以公權力, 限制你的言論自由. 但基本法不能限制你的言論自由."},{"pid":"fd9bed2292efc5bb2c71bd3a4d7d4d6b637ee368","tid":403217,"uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155605040752357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155605040752357&d=uGz%2BZe8KJa%2FUzvndc0x6sxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=a3e41742\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155605040752357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n聽到一個國字, 就以為是國家, 才會理解不到文明古國不是民族國家. 聽到一個法字, 就以為是刑法, 才會理解不到甚麼是憲. 一堆人嫌明明一個詞語就解釋完的東西, 為何要長篇大論, 但他們卻根本無法從詞語本身理解意義, 大部份時候都是腦補."},{"pid":"1f8851bf14219d6d235cf22b89a0a520051c0d5e","tid":403217,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155605032457357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155605032457357&d=uGz%2BZe8KJa%2FUzvndc0x6sxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=a068fae5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155605032457357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n言論自由不僅容許大學討論香港獨立及臺灣獨立, 亦包括香港任何地方, 任何人討論香港獨立. 而不論你是支持, 反對, 或者純粹討論其可行性, 也是在討論香港獨立. 你主張否定或反對香港獨立, 你也是使用言論自由在討論香港獨立, 都是完全合法的. 基本法是憲制文件, 憲制文件限制公權力. 他基本法亦只限制了政府的公權力實施, 故此基本法只能限制香港政府不能合法地宣佈香港獨立, 以及不能以公權力, 限制你的言論自由. 但基本法不能限制你的言論自由.</blockquote><br />\n呢段攞黎反擊份濕鳩校長聯合聲明就贏哂"},{"pid":"2431d35c8b0ad69a890dfac6ab95031f136c7607","tid":403217,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996f87bf55e457b221a4736933b675aed35d8748","tid":403217,"uid":69971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0982a03cb9eb39940071c12e7294def37fa334d2","tid":403217,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"強姦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d973bfab197132794b2e54cb34d9646c4d2af7","tid":403217,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67c2b599c29703d53b4bbcd7bc1060280a08182","tid":403217,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"你做我就執法<br />\n我做就無錯<br />\n選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03fb8e15dfca8c42a48e48a2c24f6c28fe46a27","tid":403217,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"華人智商高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}